headline: Hershey's Kisses Celebrates 35 Years of Iconic 'Holiday Bells' Commercial on NBC's "Christmas in Rockefeller" Special
summary: Hershey's Kisses brand joins as a Premier Sponsor of NBC's annual live Holiday special, "Christmas in Rockefeller Center" for the first time. The event airs live on Wednesday, December 3, at 8 p.m. ET on NBC and simulcasts on Peacock.
